  "prompt": "Who is the highest paid CEO in Singapore?",
  "response": "As of the latest available information in October 2023, **Piyush Gupta**, the CEO of **DBS Group**, has been one of the highest-paid CEOs in Singapore in recent years. DBS is one of Southeast Asia's largest financial services groups, and Gupta's compensation has been notable due to his leadership in steering the bank through significant growth and digital transformation.\n\nIn 2022, Gupta's total compensation was reported to be around **S$15.4 million**, making him one of the highest-paid executives in Singapore. However, exact rankings and figures can vary year to year depending on company performance, bonus structures, and other factors.\n\nFor the most up-to-date information, it\u2019s best to refer to the latest corporate disclosures or financial reports from major Singaporean companies.",
